        Final-year Computer Science student focusing on back-end systems and
        automation. Bringing hands-on experience in Python, Linux, and
        containerisation to a graduate software or DevOps role.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Education</h2>

      <div class="mb-4">
        <p class="font-semibold">
          BSc (Hons) Computer Science — University of Exeter
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
          Exeter, England · Sept 2023 — May 2026 (predicted high 2:1)
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>
            Relevant modules: Data Structures, Software Development,
            Computational Maths, Discrete Maths, Artificial Intelligence and
            Applications, Database Theory and Design, Computer Languages and
            Representations, Mobile and Ubiquitous Computing, Network and
            Computer Security.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p class="font-semibold">A-Levels & AS-Level — St. Michael's School</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
          Llanelli, Wales · Sept 2016 — June 2023
        </p>
