          <li>A-Levels: A* A* A — Maths, Physics, Computer Science</li>
          <li>AS-Level: A — Chemistry</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Experience</h2>

      <article>
        <p class="font-semibold">Excode Workshop Leader</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
          <a href="https://excode.co.uk" class="underline"> excode.co.uk</a> · Sept
          2025 — Nov 2025
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>Assisted in delivering beginner-friendly Python workshops.</li>
          <li>
            Mentored beginners with troubleshooting, syntax and general
            programming design.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="mb-6">
        <p class="font-semibold">
          Onboarding Assistant — Pembrokeshire County Council
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">
          Pembrokeshire, Wales · June 2024 — Sept 2024
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>
            Streamlined daily workflow by developing a Python script to automate
            data filtering, reducing manual processing time by ~60% and
            eliminating human error.
          </li>
          <li>
            Enabled system access for new employees, processing sensitive data
            in compliance with GDPR.
          </li>
          <li>Successfully managed multiple tasks concurrently.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Projects</h2>

      <article class="mb-4">
        <p class="font-semibold">Home server</p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>2-node cluster running NixOS and K3s.</li>
          <li>
            Hosts services for media, ad-blocking, web hosting, game servers and
            automations.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="mb-4">
        <p class="font-semibold">Personal Website — ed-thomas.dev</p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-5 mt-2 text-gray-700">
