          </li>
          <li>Configured and flashed the firmware.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Positions of responsibility</h2>

      <article class="mb-4">
        <p class="font-semibold">
          Social Secretary — University of Exeter Climbing Club
        </p>
