      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Skills</h2>
      <div class="text-gray-700">
        <p>
          <strong>Programming languages:</strong> Python, Java, Haskell, Nix, HTML/CSS,
          Prolog
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2">
          <strong>Technologies:</strong> Linux, Git, Docker, Kubernetes, Django,
          Astro, Google Cloud Platform
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2">
          <strong>Key competencies:</strong> Independent learning, problem-solving,
          mentoring & organisation
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
